headline: Is Tutor Perini Well-Positioned to Capitalize on Rail Megaprojects?
summary: TPC expands in U.S. rail and transit with major wins like the Manhattan tunnel and more megaprojects on the horizon.

headline: EMCOR Group, Inc. Sets Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date and Webcast
summary: NORWALK, Conn., July 17, 2025--EMCOR Group, Inc. (NYSE: EME) announced today that it will release its financial results for the second quarter ended June 30, 2025, on Thursday, July 31, 2025, prior to the market open.
